shellinabox (2.17) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Generally, SSL updates.
  * Disabling secure client-initiated renegotiation, an abused and
    unnecessary feature.
  * Added support for PFS using ECDHE.
  * Guarding build against old versions of SSL.

